description: Zsa's Gourmet Ice Cream is a small batch producer of classic and original artisanal ice cream treats. We sell our flavors by the pint and by the cup; and, sandwiched between our own gourmet cookies and baked goods. We are a mobile ice cream shop/stand, that brings delicious treats to various farmers' markets and events in the Philadelphia/Montgomery County area. CURRENT FLAVORS:Chocolate Truffle, Vanilla, Pumpkin Gingersnap, Peanut Butter, Maple Toffee Graham, Cinnamon, Rich Chocolate SorbetCURRENT ICE CREAM SANDWICHES: *Vanilla Ice Cream + Cinnamon Chocolate Chip Oatmeal Cookies*Peanut Butter Ice Cream + Double Chocolate Chip Cookies*Pumpkin Ice Cream + Gingersnap Cookies (LIMITED TIME ONLY!!)
